   LineID  PL SL  ----+-*A-1-B--+----2----+----3----+----4----+----5----+----6----+----7-|--+----8 Map and Cross Reference           
0  000058                                                                                         |                                  
   000059                FD  JOINED-FILE.                                                         |                                  
   000060                01  JN-REC.                                                              |                                  
   000061                    05  JN-OID           PIC 9(8).                                       |                                  
   000062                    05  FILLER           PIC X(1).                                       |                                  
   000063                    05  JN-CID           PIC 9(6).                                       |                                  
   000064                    05  FILLER           PIC X(1).                                       |                                  
   000065                    05  JN-NAME          PIC X(20).                                      |                                  
   000066                    05  FILLER           PIC X(1).                                       |                                  
   000067                    05  JN-AMT           PIC 9(9).                                       |                                  
   000068                                                                                         |                                  
   000069                WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                                 |                                  
   000070                                                                                         |                                  
   000071               *--- sizing (primary load = N-CUST / (NBKT*BSLOTS) ) -------------        |                                  
   000072               *    plain data items: IBM COBOL 1.2.0 has no level-78 constants.         |                                  
   000073               *    OCCURS below uses the matching integer literals (640 / 8 / 768).     |                                  
   000074                01  NBKT                 PIC 9(3) VALUE 640.                             |                                  
   000075                01  BSLOTS               PIC 9    VALUE 8.                               |                                  
   000076                01  OVF-CAP              PIC 9(3) VALUE 768.                             |                                  
   000077                01  N-CUST               PIC 9(4) VALUE 4608.                            |                                  
   000078                01  N-ORDER              PIC 9(5) VALUE 18432.                           |                                  
   000079                01  CUST-BASE            PIC 9(6) VALUE 100000.                          |                                  
   000080                                                                                         |                                  
   000081               *--- the dereference table : NBKT buckets x BSLOTS slots ---------        |                                  
   000082                01  PRIMARY-STORE.                                                       |                                  
   000083                    05  P-BUCKET OCCURS 640 TIMES.                                       |                                  
   000084                        10  P-SLOT OCCURS 8 TIMES.                                       |                                  
   000085                            15  P-KEY    PIC 9(6).                                       |                                  
   000086                            15  P-NAME   PIC X(20).                                      |                                  
   000087                01  BUCKET-OCC.                                                          |                                  
   000088                    05  B-OCC OCCURS 640 TIMES PIC 9(2).                                 |                                  
   000089                                                                                         |                                  
   000090               *--- the backup table : a small linear-probe overflow region ----         |                                  
   000091                01  OVERFLOW-STORE.                                                      |                                  
   000092                    05  O-CELL OCCURS 768 TIMES.                                         |                                  
   000093                        10  O-KEY        PIC 9(6).                                       |                                  
   000094                        10  O-NAME       PIC X(20).                                      |                                  
   000095                                                                                         |                                  
   000096               *--- file status ------------------------------------------------         |                                  
   000097                01  CUST-STATUS          PIC XX VALUE SPACES.                            |IMP                               
   000098                    88  CUST-OK          VALUE '00'.                                     |                                  
   000099                    88  CUST-EOF         VALUE '10'.                                     |                                  
   000100                01  ORD-STATUS           PIC XX VALUE SPACES.                            |IMP                               
   000101                    88  ORD-OK           VALUE '00'.                                     |                                  
   000102                    88  ORD-EOF          VALUE '10'.                                     |                                  
   000103                01  JN-STATUS            PIC XX VALUE SPACES.                            |IMP                               
   000104                                                                                         |                                  
   000105               *--- loop / scratch ---------------------------------------------         |                                  
   000106                01  WS-EOF               PIC X VALUE 'N'.                                |                                  
   000107                    88  EOF-YES          VALUE 'Y'.                                      |                                  
   000108                01  WS-I                 PIC 9(9).                                       |                                  
   000109                01  WS-J                 PIC 9(4).                                       |                                  
   000110                01  WS-S                 PIC 9(6).                                       |                                  
   000111                01  WS-BKT               PIC 9(4).                                       |                                  
   000112                01  WS-OH                PIC 9(6).                                       |                                  
   000113                01  WS-STMP              PIC 9(9).                                       |                                  
   000114                01  WS-HV                PIC 9(18).                                      |                                  
